data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to 301 Kiwanis Circle, Chuluota, FL 32766, a captivating single-family residence that seamlessly blends comfort and elegance. This customized home, situated on an expansive 1.86 acre property, offers a unique and personalized living experience. Beyond the confines of the home, residents have exclusive access to a vast expanse of land, perfect for those who appreciate outdoor activities. The property features an 18-hole disc golf course, providing endless opportunities for recreation and enjoyment. This charming home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing a perfect haven for families or those seeking a serene living space. Step inside and be greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior featuring ceiling fans throughout, creating a cool and inviting atmosphere. The living room/dining room combo offers a versatile space for both relaxation and entertaining, with ample natural light illuminating the room. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with appliances that include a dishwasher, dryer, microwave, range, refrigerator, and washer. The solid surface counters and solid wood cabinets add a touch of sophistication to the heart of the home, offering both style and functionality. One of the highlights of this property is the private pool, which provides a refreshing oasis right at your doorstep. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in the inviting in-ground pool, surrounded by a screen enclosure that adds an extra layer of comfort and privacy to your outdoor experience. Whether you're lounging by the pool, enjoying the extensive land, or playing a round of disc golf, 301 Kiwanis Circle is designed to cater to your every need. This residence seamlessly combines amenities, creating a home that is both stylish and functional. Additional county information reveals that the property relies on well water and a septic tank system, ensuring self-sufficiency and a connection to the natural surroundings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful residence your home, where customized features, extensive outdoor amenities, and a touch of luxury come together seamlessly. Zoned Agriculture.
